Class Calle

java.lang.Object
CLASES.Casilla
CLASES.Calle
All Implemented Interfaces:
Efectos
Direct Known Subclasses:
Estacion, Normal
public abstract class Calle extends Casilla
Abstract class representing a property in the game. It contains common attributes and methods for properties such as name, rent, price, and owner. The class also defines the effect of landing on the property, which can either be buying it or paying rent.
